Status is clean when file changes case
  $ newclientrepo
  $ touch file
  $ hg commit -Aqm foo
  $ mv file FILE
  $ hg st

Status keeps removed file and untracked file separate
  $ newclientrepo
  $ touch file
  $ hg commit -Aqm foo
  $ hg rm file
  $ touch FILE
